//! Empty same-named `Source` module.
//!
//! Declares a `Source` trait with NO associated types. It shares the bare name
//! `Source` with `hew::assocreq`'s trait (which DOES require `type Item`). When
//! both are imported, the global bare `trait_defs["Source"]` is last-write-wins;
//! the required-associated-type enforcement must not read that bare entry, or an
//! impl of `assocreq.Source` that omits `Item` is accepted whenever this empty
//! `Source` happens to win the write.

/// A same-named `Source` with no associated types.
pub trait Source {
}
